{"word":"G3861 - παράδοξος - parádoxos - par-ad'-ox-os - Strange","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παράδοξος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parádoxos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ad'-ox-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Strange</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதிசயமான காரியங்கள் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unexpected, uncommon, incredible, wonderful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1391 - δόξα - dóxa - dox'-ah/1391\">G1391</a> (in the sense of <i>seeming</i>); <i>contrary to expectation</i>, that is, <i>extraordinary</i> (&ldquo;paradox&rdquo;): - strange.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1380/1380\">G1380</a>, <a href=\"#/G1391/1391\">G1391</a>, <a href=\"#/G1392/1392\">G1392</a>, <a href=\"#/G1740/1740\">G1740</a>, <a href=\"#/G1741/1741\">G1741</a>, <a href=\"#/G3861/3861\">G3861</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888/4888\">G4888</a>"}]}